long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
OneBook helps you in creating notes while learning coding online.
You can refer these notes after completing the video to write the code in your compiler.

By using OneBook, you no longer have to switch tabs again and again while watching video.

How to use OneBook?
After Installing the extension, Press Command B on Mac and Control B on Windows to take notes.
Go to website onebook.digital to revise from the notes.
